hopobject.body: magic story very thanks pai health app But none the less the chocolate world is going mad for small-scale producers who are buying in cocoa beans and making the brown ambrosia from scratch, often in tiny quantities. This micro-produced chocolate isn’t necessarily better than what the big guys make – but it is more interesting and diverse, with individual producers allowing the flavours of very small batches of beans from individual areas to emerge.
